title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

Customize your own dinosaur collection: Collect LEGO amber and experiment with DNA to create completely original dinosaurs, like the Dilophosaurus Rex. 
 
Populate and explore Isla Nublar and Isla Sorna: Put your unique dinosaur creations in to paddocks as you complete special Free Play missions.

By the time we made up (and he let me see the receipts), it was just past the return policy so NONE of it could be returned so I boxed everything up & put it in the closet until now. It is all in perfect looking condition, no scratches or dings etc as everything was kept in our entertainment nook for 10 months & then packed up & put away when he bought the new system. We "wiped" the console memory clean (he didn't have much on it to begin with) so it is totally ready to use. Our house is filling up w/stuff & we now have a Toddler (a Daughter who isn't going to play video games) who also has a lot of stuff & we are running out of room so we are selling a bunch of stuff including the original Xbox 360 system & other duplicate accessories & games for the system. None of the below was even used for 12 months when I boxed everything up. 
 
 -Included in the original box & details from the box are the following (1st & 2nd pic): 
 -Xbox 360 S Console (Black Gloss). 
 -250GB Hard Drive (Includes Game & Demos). 
 -Xbox 360 Wireless Controller (in perfect condition as we had a blue controller cover on it which we are keeping for the new COD controller). 
 -Composite AV Cable (Standard Definition). 
 -Xbox 360 Headset. 
 -Internal WiFi Capability. 
 -Xbox Live; Online Games, Movies, Music & Entertainment Service w/access to Zune, Facebook, Netflix, Twitter, Last.FM & Windows Media Center. 
 -Watch your own DVD's as well on this Xbox 360 Console. 
 -"With the largest library of Games and the best in HD Movies & TV, nothing brings people together like Xbox 360!". 
 -All original paperwork/Manual's that came in the original box. 
 -All the above cost us $330.00 including tax (1st & 2nd pics). 
 
 -Additional Accessories & Games purchased separately but included in this deal are the following (3rd & 4th pics): 
 -A second Xbox 360 Wireless Controller (in perfect condition as we had a pink controller cover on it which we are keeping for the new COD controller). 
 -A second Xbox 360 Headset (Brand new, never used as it came w/the COD package but he bought a high-tech Headset to use w/the COD Console so we are selling this other Headset). 
 -Nyko Xbox 360 S two Controller Charge Base including two rechargeable Batteries (this is another duplicate). 
 -High Speed HDMI Cable (this is another duplicate). 
 -The following 5 games of which each one is in great condition & have hardly been played/used. I can take pics of the backs if you'd like, I didn't think about it till now. Just let me know. 
 1. Call of Duty, MW3 (Modern Warfare), Rated M. Comes w/all paperwork/Manual. 
 2. EA Sports, NHL10, Rated E. Comes w/all paperwork/Manual. 
 3. Madden, NFL 07, Rated E. (In plain purple case). 
 4. Shaun White, Snowboarding, Limited Edition, Rated T. Comes w/all paperwork/Manual. I honestly think my Husband played this game once, MAYBE twice after we bought it & hasn't touched it since. 
 5. Hulk Hogan's Main Event, Rated T. Comes w/all paperwork/manual. I think he only tried this game once & never touched it again. 
 -Everything in this paragraph cost us $320.00 including tax (3rd & 4th pics). 
 
 I just took these pictures & put everything back in boxes (the original Xbox 360 box & a brown box) & with that, you have everything needed to plug in the Console & Controller Charging Base & start playing w/two players! Nothing else is needed! We bought everything retail, brand new so we are the original & only owners of everything listed above. Everything is like new as it was hardly played & only by my Husband & once in awhile by myself (no kids or friends etc to damage anything). This is a package deal & a great splurge for yourself/Family or a great gift for your Loved ones since it's in the original Xbox 360 packaging! We paid $650.00 including tax for everything in this ad & may be able to meet you somewhere for your convenience depending on where you are in the Valley versus you driving to our house so knowing these things, please contact me ASAP w/your best offer. Thank you.

title: GRID 2 XBOX 360
description: In pre-production for two years, GRID 2 is in full development on the evolution of the award-winning EGO game technology platform. Following the success of GRID, which set the standards for damage, AI, visuals and introduced the flashback time rewind feature adopted by many racing games. GRID 2 will again raise the gameplay and technological bar for motorsport gaming and remain true to the series' core value. It is all about the race. In an expansive career mode, players will experience aggressive wheel-to-wheel racing against advanced AI where each spectacular race unfolds with cinematic immersion. Building on the handling model from GRID, the truefeel handling system will use real physics to hit a sweetspot between accessibility and simulation and deliver handling that is approachable yet challenging to master.

title: MIdnight Club Los Angeles Complete Edition XBOX 360
description: Midnight Club: Los Angeles is the latest game in the frantically fast open-city racing franchise. Set in a stunning recreation of 'The City of Angels'. Midnight Club: Los Angeles is Rockstar San Diego's most ambitious offering yet. It runs on their internally developed RAGE technology (Rockstar Advanced Game Engine), which offers a level of quality that has previously been unimaginable on next-generation consoles. Not only does this new technology allow for breathtakingly beautiful surroundings that rip past your eyes as you tear through the LA traffic, but also it allows for the largest ever fully open city playground for you to race through. Complete with fully licensed cars from a wide range of top manufacturers, and extensive customization options, Midnight Club: Los Angeles also offers an innovative system of progression bringing unparalleled freedom of choice to how your own unique experience unfolds. No racing game will compare to the exhilarating 'no rules' experience of driving illegally through this incredibly detailed, open world environment of the real city of LA. With high-octane online play and a cutting-edge soundtrack Midnight Club: Los Angeles will be the definitive next generation racing game.

* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port

* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: xbox360 and games Perfect condition
description:
xBox360 S system with accessories and all connections    $195 
3 controllers, 14 games, Perfect working condition 
 
The newly redesigned 250 GB Xbox 360 upgrades your entire Xbox 360 gaming experience, with a leaner profile, more ports, plenty of storage space and built-in Wi-Fi that makes it easier for you to enjoy Xbox LIVE games, HD movies, streaming TV and more. It's also ready to pair up with Kinect, the revolutionary sensor that makes you the controller. It all adds up to more games, more entertainment and more fun. 
 
Built-in Wi-Fi: The Xbox S 360 is the only console with 802.11n Wi-Fi built-in for a faster and easier connection to Xbox LIVE. Stream HD movies and TV or download games from Xbox LIVE in 1080p and 5.1 surround sound from anywhere in the house. Compatible with b/g/n networks. 
250GB Hard Drive: The internal, removable 250GB hard drive offers plenty of space to save games, HD TV and movies, music, pictures, game add-ons, demos and more. 
Kinect Ready: Kinect brings games and entertainment to life in extraordinary new ways - no controller required. Easy to use and instantly fun, Kinect gets everyone off the couch moving, laughing and cheering. See a ball? Kick it. Want to join a friend in the fun? Simply jump in. Even control an HD movie with a wave of the hand. Featuring a dedicated, specialized port, the Xbox 360 250GB is built to connect seamlessly with the Kinect Sensor.* 
More ports: Connect more accessories and storage solutions with added USB ports. Now with a total of 5, (3 back/2 front) you'll find more places to plug and play. Plus, in addition to the standard Ethernet port and HDMI output, we've added an integrated optical audio out port for an easier connection to the booming sound of your A/V receiver. 
 
No emails  Text or call Olivia

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

This is a rare and collectible Texas Land Grant signed by Sam Houston, the Father of Texas. The document is signed 1860, making it a pre-civil war document. The document is framed with a museum quality frame and matts. The display also includes two portraits of Sam Houston as General in the Republic of Texas army. In one portrait, Houston is pictured on Horseback at the Battle of San Jacinto. The other is from a period painting of Houston. The display also includes an elegant brass plaque engraved with the famous Houston quote, "Texas Has Yet to Learn Submission to Any Oppression, Come From What Source It May". Sam Houston had a "common" signature, and an "ornate" signature. This document has his ornate signature. He would sign his name in such a way that it looks like he is singing "I Am Houston". That is, in the ornate signature, the "S" in sam looks like an "I". In any event, it is an ornate and flamboyant signature. This piece is available only for local sale . . . I can not ship this piece. If you have any questions, or would like to see it, let me know. It would make an incredible gift for any Texas History Buff, or anyone looking to dress up an office or study. It is extremely rare, and will definitely be a conversation piece. title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
ONE CALL 
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
JUST MAKE A CALL 
  
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT?
  
 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
CALL ME NOW 
  
 
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.

title: BROKEN XBOX ONE AND PS4???BLOD??HDMI PORT??!!!!!!!
description:
CALL NOW 
  
 
* If your PS4 turns on and the white light comes on but there is no picture on the TV 
* Bent or broken pins inside the HDMI port 
* The TV might say "no signal" or something similar with the console hooked up via the HDMI cable 
* A crooked port or one that looks like it's been pushed in further than it should be. 
 
HOW TO FIX A PS4 HDMI PORT? 
 
The ports on these consoles can be extremely difficult to repair unless you have expert level soldering and electronics repair skills. They are soldered onto the motherboard with 4 main pins with lots of solder, then they also have 19 very small pins that also have to be soldered onto solder pads on the motherboard. 
 
The only good and permanent fix for a bad HDMI port is to replace the entire port. Some of them just have pins that have been pushed back so they no longer make contact with the pins on the cable. Even though many times you can push these pins back, there is no good way to keep them there. The whole port needs to be replaced in order to fix this permanently. 
 
We offer an HDMI port fix that is reliable. We have the experience to repair your PS4 correctly and quickly the first time. We fix dozens of these and have a very high success rate.
